  <Name>Jerserra's Influence</Name>
  <Description>[H4]Force Power: Jerserre's Influence[h4]
Jerserra combined her Inquisitor's strict training with her guidance from her shard of the Nardithi Cluster and found a way to project fear onto her foes. Other Force users, through encountering Jerserra and her power, can learn to do the same.
[P]The user may spend [FP] to target one character within short range. That character must immediately make an [B]Average ([DI][DI]) fear check as an out of turn incidental. The user may not activate this multiple times.
</Description>
